meta {
  name: Get Following
  type: http
  seq: 3
}

get {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/api/users/:userId/following
  body: none
  auth: none
}

params:path {
  userId: 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
}

params:query {
  page: 0
  size: 20
  sort: pseudo,asc
}

docs {
  # Get Following

  Returns a paginated list of users that the specified user follows.

  ## Authentication

  No authentication required.

  ## Path Parameters

  - **userId**: The UUID of the user whose following list to retrieve

  ## Query Parameters

  | Parameter | Type | Default | Description |
  |-----------|------|---------|-------------|
  | page | Integer | 0 | Page number (0-based) |
  | size | Integer | 20 | Page size (max 100) |
  | sort | String | pseudo,asc | Sort criteria (field,direction) |

  ## Response (200 OK)

  ```json
  {
    "content": [
      {
        "id": "uuid",
        "pseudo": "username",
        "picture": "url"
      }
    ],
    "metadata": {
      "page": 0,
      "size": 20,
      "totalElements": 1,
      "totalPages": 1,
      "first": true,
      "last": true,
      "hasNext": false,
      "hasPrevious": false
    }
  }
  ```

  ## Error Responses

  - **404 Not Found**: User does not exist
}
